<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ871224-0159 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:Coleco Industries Inc.</HL><DD> 12/24/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> CLO WNEWS </IN><DATELINE> COLECO INDUSTRIES INC. (West Hartford, Conn.)  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Paul C. Meyer was named executive vice president and chief financial officer of this toy and game maker. He succeeds Karl Slacik, who resigned in November to pursue a financial consulting practice, the company said. Mr. Meyer formerly was executive vice president, administration. </TEXT></DOC>